                    </div>
                    <span>Who let Cafardo write this book<P>To truly understand how magical the Pats title was...one would have had to believe.<P>Cafardo didn't<P>Heck, as much as I hate The Curly Haired Boyfriend Dan Shaugnessey....he would have given this team it's proper poetic justice</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">My daughter writes better</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
