                    <span>The Cinderella season of the patriots is captured magnificently in this book. "The Impossible Team" takes you back to the glorious season that shocked the NFL. Nick Cafardo's great storytelling coupled with the key interviews and comments from all involved makes this a can't pass up book if your a new england sports fan.</span>
                  
              
